oreover, N is uniquely determined modulo rs. An equivalent statement is tha=
t if (r,s)=3D1, then every pair of residue classes modulo r and s correspon=
ds to a simple residue class modulo rs. The Chinese remainder theorem is im=
plemented in the Wolfram Language as ChineseRemainder[{a1, a2, ...}{m1, m2,=
 ...}]. The...">
